quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"We sent this [Qur'an] down during the Night of Decree"
  97,2,But how would you know what is the Night of Decree
  97,3,The Night of Decree is better than a thousand months
  97,4,"During that Night, the angels and the Spirit descend by their Lord's authority for a variety of matters"
  97,5,There is peace that night until the coming of dawn